question: Show me frequent flyer lounges and VIP lounges with complimentary Wi-Fi.
sql_query1:
SELECT Lounge.Name 
FROM Lounge
WHERE (Lounge.exclusiveArea = "Frequent Flyer Lounge" OR Lounge.exclusiveArea = "VIP Lounge") AND Lounge.amenities = "Complimentary Wi-Fi"
sql_query2:
SELECT Lounge.Name 
FROM Lounge
WHERE Lounge.exclusiveArea = "Frequent Flyer Lounge" OR Lounge.exclusiveArea = "VIP Lounge" AND Lounge.amenities = "Complimentary Wi-Fi"
interpretation1: Which frequent flyer lounges have complimentary Wi-Fi and which VIP lounges have the same amenity?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all frequent flyer lounges and also provide a list of VIP lounges with complimentary Wi-Fi.
